                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "My Dearling Shawn...",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "2f606d1b-40f4-4aee-aac7-e3cc3b4aac3e",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "'Tis so very happy I am to hear that you are at the Hero University. I can't tell you how proud it makes me feel to know that you have a chance at a brighter future.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "a0c55a7a-4caa-4171-a7dc-b284b00e3ce0",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Take care of yourself there at the school. Be sure to make some new friends. Don't forget to study hard so that you can get good grades and a good job when you graduate.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "22304cd0-48c0-4bad-9408-4c85ad679922",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Your dad would be so very proud of you, too.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c6725f28-da77-428c-8c9a-6b619d355939",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Your loving mother, Nora",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "90bd6cb0-4ffb-463c-a71a-debf45e1f3e4",
                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Well, maybe I should at least try to take this school seriously... It would make Mama happy.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "729973c6-6395-49c7-b7e0-3a9c63bc6acd",
                    "name": "Letter From Mom",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "<i>My Dearling Shawn,\n\n'Tis so very happy I am to hear that you are at the Hero University. I can't tell you how proud it makes me feel to know that you have a chance at a brighter future.\n\nTake care of yourself there at the school. Be sure to make some new friends. Don't forget to study hard so that you can get good grades and a good job when you graduate. \n\nYour dad would be so very proud of you, too.\n\nYour loving mother,\nNora</i>"
                },
